script.name: !move.movetosector
script.description: Fly ship to a sector, jump enabled
script.sourceplaintext:
$target = $targetsector if is datatype[ $target ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $targetsector = $target[3] else if $targetsector -> exists if $targetsector -> is of class Ship $targetsector = $target -> get sector else if $targetsector -> is of class Station $targetsector = $target -> get sector end end
if not $targetsector -> exists return FLRET_INVALIDPARMS end
* cant fly throgh gates ? always jump if theres a jump beacon if not [THIS] ->can fly through gates * first check we have energy skip if [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay return FLRET_NOPATH
if $targetsector ->sector has jumpable jump beacons: ship=[THIS] $flags = [Find.JumpBeacons] | [Find.ExcludeGates] | [Find.ExcludeTerranGates] do if [OWNER] == Player $flags = $flags | [Find.Known] $beacons = find gate: flags=$flags, refobj=$targetsector, max dist=null, refpos=null object check=[THIS] if is datatype[ $beacons ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $beacon = get random array item: array=$beacons else $beacon = $beacons end end
* if not beacon in sector, we need to place one if not $beacon -> exists if not [THIS] -> get amount of ware Jump Beacon in cargo bay if not [THIS] -> get amount of ware Single-Use Jump Beacon in cargo bay return FLRET_NOPATH end end * we need docked ship or recon drone to place beacon if not [THIS] -> get amount of ware Recon Drone in cargo bay $docked.ships = [THIS] ->get ship table from sector/ship/station skip if $docked.ships return FLRET_NOPATH skip if size of table $docked.ships return FLRET_NOPATH end end
* we know we can get there, now we need fuel $energy = [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $needed = [THIS] -> needed jump drive energy for jump to sector $targetsector $needed = $needed - $energy if $needed > 0 * attempt to resupply $resupply = [THIS] -> get jumpdrive fuel resupply do if $resupply $resupply = [THIS] ->get needed jump energy: jumps=$resupply $cargo.free = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $cargo.free = $cargo.free / 10 do if $cargo.free > 200 $cargo.free = 200 $needed = get maximum, $needed, $resupply, $cargo.free, null, null @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.resupply.self : Ware to Resupply=Energy Cells Quantity=$needed Max Fly Range=5
$energy = [THIS] -> get amount of ware Energy Cells in cargo bay $needed = [THIS] -> needed jump drive energy for jump to sector $targetsector * resupply failed ? we cant get there now if $needed > $energy return FLRET_NOPATH end end
* do we need to deploy the beacon? if not $beacon -> exists @ skip if [THIS] -> call script !lib.deploybeacon.and.jump : Target Sector=$targetsector return FLRET_NOPATH else do if [THIS] -> is of class Carrier @ = [THIS] -> call script !carrier.recall : @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.jump : gate or sector=$beacon followers should jump too=null end do if [SECTOR] == $targetsector return FLRET_OK return FLRET_NOPATH end
* Different handling for player ships, to make use of global blacklist $route = null if [OWNER] == Player if $target -> exists if $target -> is of class Sector $target = [THIS] -> get destination skip if $target -> exists $target = $targetsector end end
@ $route = [THIS] -> call script !lib.player.saferoute : Destination=$target Ignore Jump=[FALSE] Always Jump=[FALSE] Additional Blacklist=null Ignore Fuel=[FALSE] Allow Table=null do if $route == [TRUE] return FLRET_OK
skip if $route return FLRET_NOPATH
do if [THIS] -> is of class Carrier @ = [THIS] -> call script !carrier.recall :
do if [THIS] -> is docked @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.undock :
$skip.to.sector = [FALSE]
$size = size of array $route $i = 0 while $i < $size $dest = $route[$i] $sector = $dest -> get sector inc $i =
if $skip.to.sector if $sector == [SECTOR] $skip.to.sector = [FALSE] end continue end
if $sector != [SECTOR] @ if [THIS] -> call script !move.autojump : Destination=$dest do if $sector == [SECTOR] continue end $dest = $dest -> get gate destination: return sector=[FALSE] end
do if $targetsector == [SECTOR] return FLRET_OK
$dest.sector = $dest -> get gate destination: return sector=[TRUE] if $dest.sector == [SECTOR] $dest.sector = $dest -> get sector end
@ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector.simple : sector=$dest.sector if $ret == FLRET_INTERRUPTED OR $ret == FLRET_BREAK if [SECTOR] != $dest.sector $target.jumps = get jumps from sector [SECTOR] to sector $targetsector $jumps = get jumps from sector $dest.sector to sector $targetsector if $target.jumps > $jumps @ = wait 1 ms dec $i = continue else $skip.to.sector = [TRUE] end end end end
if $skip.to.sector AND [SECTOR] != $targetsector @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector.simple : sector=$targetsector end
return FLRET_OK
else @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetosector.route : sector=$targetsector return $ret end
return null
